NEW: Senate bill prohibiting #2020census from asking abt citizenship/immigration status has been introduced by @SenatorMenendez (D-NJ).

@SenCortezMasto (D-Nev.) says it would "ensure the Census takes a full & accurate account of our nation’s population.”

